  "description": "Recommendation tray (\"We think you'll love these\") for the Nordstrom Price Drop Shopping Bag email. Eight-tile grid driven by a recommendation service keyed on the profile shopperId. PLACEHOLDER: the rec-service base URL, API key, and placement are stubbed with REPLACE_ME values to be filled in manually; each tile links via a per-slot offset (0-7). Section vocabulary \"RecTray\" is provisional and pending governance sign-off.",
  "fragment": {
